text: Hello all! I'm Redante, based in Rockville, Maryland near Washington DC in the US. I work as a <https://www.linkedin.com/in/redante|digital communications manager> for an international nonprofit organization managing websites and email marketing. On the side I am starting with <https://www.clippings.me/redante|freelance writing>. I aspire to be a B2B writer for tech companies who serve medium to large nonprofits. Glad to be part of this community and can't wait to interact with everyone!

text: Hi everyone, I'm Melita, from Jakarta, Indonesia. So great to find this community :slightly_smiling_face: I work as Content Manager for a local start-up fintech company. I've been a Content Writer and Copywriter (at other places) for around 3 years, but actually last year was my first time as a Content Manager. Moving from execution to managing content and strategic thinking, it's a really new thing for me and it's been quite a growth curve. The courses on Superpath Pro has been super helpful, and I hope to have a great co-learning experience with everyone in the Slack community as well. Thank you!
